Trinket: Reduce incoming damage.
Trinket: Heal Heart(s) when entering a shop.
Weapon: Shoot bubbles to capture enemies and push them back. Deals damage when popped. Will aim at random target.
Weapon: Hit enemies in an arc around you. Will aim the the closest enemy if possible.
Trinket: Look cool and stylish while dealing extra damage with more critical chance and critical damage.
Heal 1 Heart.
Weapon: Thow knives at enemies. Will target enemies in range.
Increase your character level by 1. Increase damage, movement speed, critical chance and damage over time.
PROTEIN! GET YOUR MUSCLE ON AND DO MORE DAMAGE WITH PROTEIN!
Weapon: Spawn tornados at random poritions on the map that move towards you.
Woah, woah, woah, woah, woah! What's going on here?
Why are you not dead? What is the meaning of this?
Who are you anyways? You know what? I don't care. I'm just gonna make sur this doesn't happen again.
Let's reset this and see what we can do. So, 3 hearts? Check. Zero coins? Check. Remove "weapons"? Check. Get rid of the "trinkets?" Check.
Ok, you've done that enough. Let's see if you can do it again.
And off to the start you go!
It seems I have misjudged you. A mistake I will not do a second time.
It is time to remove the kid gloves. Lets see if you can do this with even more enemies.
It seems, that also was a waste. Time for some more drastic measures.
Let's see if the future can content with you. Well, your future that is.
Wu.. How? Who?
Alright. Let's crank the difficulty up again!
[shake]ARRGGH![/shake] WHAT IS THE MEANING OF THIS?!?!
YOU SHALL KNOW THE [pulse]WRATH[/pulse] OF [shake][ghost]DEATH[/ghost][/shake]! ONE DOES NOT SIMPLY WALK INTO MY DOMAIN!
To the past. And let's make sur you can't do much!
HOW?! You have the worst weapon possible! OK! No more Mister Nice Death. No weapons, no chance!
Please stop. No more. I give up. You win. I can't kill you. You can't die. Whatever is going on, I don't like it.
Let's just call it quits and never speak of this ever again. Ok?
Ok, bye.
